<template>
  <v-container class="fill-height" fluid>
    <v-layout justify-center align-center>
      <v-flex xs6>
        <v-img :src="image" class="my-3" height="120" contain />
      </v-flex>
    </v-layout>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
import imageGif from "@/assets/img/loading_econet.09ae85d0.gif";
import Auth from "@/services/modules/auth.js";
import { mapGetters } from "vuex";

export default {
  name: "Autenticar",
  data: function () {
    return {
      image: imageGif,
    };
  },
  created() {
    // this.changeToken()
  },
  mounted() {
    localStorage.clear();

    //chamar classe para gerarToken();
    let auth = new Auth();
    let autenticao = auth.generateToken();
    let that = this;

    Promise.resolve(autenticao).then(function () {
      let dados = {
        id: localStorage.getItem('id_usuario') ? localStorage.getItem('id_usuario') : 0,
      };

      //verificar termo de uso
      that.$store.dispatch("termo/verificaTermo", dados).then((response) => {
        if (response.status == 200) {
          localStorage.setItem("aceite_termo", true);
        } else {
          localStorage.removeItem("aceite_termo");
        }
      });
    });
  },
  computed: {
    ...mapGetters("auth", {
      id_usuario: "getIdUsuario",
    }),
  },
  methods: {},
};
</script>
